passive.name: New Chapter
passive.description: Increases the wearer's DEF by <orangeStrong>{{1, percent}}%</orangeStrong>. Increases the DMG of the wearer when they use their Ultimate by <orangeStrong>{{2, percent}}%</orangeStrong> of the wearer's DEF. This effect only applies 1 time per enemy target during each use of the wearer's Ultimate.
